description: Nicolette is sweet, young and very innocent...exactly the type of girl we like to corrupt here at WaterBondage! After being ordered to place herself in cuffs she realises that she has given up all control, including the choice of when and how she cums. Nicolette suffers beautifully but finds the ICE to be too difficult, once untied she challenges Chanta to brave the ICE!
title: Nicolette
